            <h1><span href="#sectionThree">V</span></h1>
          <div class="projoOneIntro">
            <h1>Javascript Game</h1>
            <p>An audio visual memory game</p>
          </div>
          <div class="projoOneDesc hidden">
            <p>For this game I wanted to create something which was both fun to play and visually stimulating. I chose to make a multiplayer audio visual memory game. To play, you must repeat back the computer's sequence by hitting the keys in the right order. Get the sequence right to progress to the next round. As my first build, I challenged myself to create something which involved some challenging game logic and time based functionality- allowing me to learn as much as possible during the build.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <p><a href="https://github.com/mikejdegroot/project-0" target="_blank">GitHub</a> || <a href="https://tranquil-anchorage-93539.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank">Heroku</a></p>
            </div>
