    <section id="sectionSix">
      <div class="spotlightOverlay">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="projoFourDesc col-lg-4 offset-lg-1">
            <h1>Social Issues Forum</h1>
            <p>A discussion forum for social issues. Users can post articles they think need to be discussed, comment on other people's articles and tag other users in the discussion for cohesive conversation. Once tagged, a user receives a notification in their nav bar and is directed to the article they were tagged in. My second group project- built with a Ruby on Rails backend and an Angular Front End, the biggest challenge here was creating the notifications functionality, allowing users to tag each other and receive notifications. The notification functionality really adds to the realism of the site and adds a lot of value for users.</p>
          </div>
